  </section>

  <!-- Botones de redes sociales -->

  <section class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-8 lg:px-20 py-12 space-y-8 text-left text-gray-800 tracking-tight transition duration-300 ease-in-out">

    <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold">About Me</h1>
    
    <p class="text-base lg:text-lg">
      I’m Elvis, a passionate IT professional originally from Maracaibo, Venezuela 🇻🇪, now based in Madrid, Spain. My journey in tech has been driven by a relentless curiosity and a knack for solving complex problems.
    </p>
  
    <p class="text-base lg:text-lg">
      With a background in <span class="text-orange-500 font-bold">Electronic Engineering</span> focused on Automation and Process Control, I've pivoted into IT, cloud infrastructure, and DevOps. My expertise isn't confined to theoretical knowledge—I thrive on implementing practical solutions that drive impact.
    </p>
  
    <p class="text-base lg:text-lg">
      Currently, I’m part of the team at 
      <strong class="text-orange-500 hover:underline decoration-gray-400 font-bold">
        <a href="http://paloaltonetworks.com" target="_blank">Palo Alto Networks↗</a>
      </strong>, where I work closely with customers, ensuring their cloud security! 😶‍🌫️


    </p>
  
    <p class="text-base lg:text-lg">
      What sets me apart is my ability to bridge the gap between engineering and IT operations. I’m a proactive problem solver who doesn’t shy away from challenges—whether it’s streamlining cloud infrastructure, automating processes, or enhancing security frameworks.
    </p>
  
    <p class="text-base lg:text-lg">
      I’m not just about the tech—I bring creativity, adaptability, and a results-driven mindset to every project. My experience across different countries has sharpened my ability to adapt and excel in diverse environments.
    </p>

    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-1 gap-4">
        <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-orange-500 mb-4">Technologies</h3>
        <ul class="space-y-2">
            <li>• GCP & AWS and Azure</l>
            <li>• Terraform & CloudFormation</li>
            <li>• Kubernetes & Docker</li>
            <li>• CI/CD Pipelines</li>
            <li>• Cloud-Native Application Protection Platform (CNAPP)</li>
            <li>• IAM & Secrets Management</li>
            <li>• WAF & OWASP</li>
            <li>• Compliance (CIS, ISO)</li>
            <li>• Python & Bash</li>
            <li>• Git</li>
            <li>• YAML & JSON</li>
            <li>• Postman & APIs</li>
        </ul>
      </div>


      <p class="text-lg font-bold text-orange-500 mt-10">
        Ready to take your project to the next level?
      </p>
    
      <p class="text-base lg:text-lg">
        Let’s make it happen. If you’re looking for a technical expert with a creative edge, I’m here to help. Reach out via 
        <a href="mailto:e.finol7@gmail.com" class="text-orange-500 underline">email</a>—let’s build something great together!
      </p>
  
  </section>


  
</Layout>